reviews.text: Classic Seaside Town. Loved It! Recommend a visit for all Traditional Seaside frivolity!!

I have had to change train tickets to London due to the Thomas Cook crash the staff could not have been more helpful or patient
You dont need to use trainline they will match prices and give you expert assistance

Nice station you can catch trains to central liverpool blackburn hunts cross liverpool airport and leeds. They have two companies operating at this station and the toilets are descent. They have a little shop where tou can buy some snacks, drinks and tickets. Nice place!

The station is in a really good location to visit the shops. Very clean and normally staff are helpful. However on my last visit when I asked one of the staff for the time of the next train he told me to look at the display board.  My eyesight isnt very good  but I managed.
